Open `mongosh` and run the insert commands from [Section 4](#4-database-setup-mongodb).

### Step 3 — Start the Backend

```bash
cd backend
node server.js
# Server starts on http://localhost:7000
```

### Step 4 — Start the Frontend

```bash
cd frontend/pizzeria
ng serve
# App starts on http://localhost:4200
```

